{"tid":1448910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:58.000Z","uid":110729,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1af39c09a48af185bb902bb0cc477555a9e844b1","tid":1448910,"uid":110729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:42.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場"},{"pid":"5286fe8132dd14121aac2fef43ec5cd5e2632c5e","tid":1448910,"uid":296928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0b08653d6d858216b673321542f56d480a757a4","tid":1448910,"uid":84614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18c7b9da8c6db5eeb8fdddba75b673d380792e3e","tid":1448910,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2127f7113916bfce8fff8369ed50928176c40771","tid":1448910,"uid":195443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f8f3814f1d847b2cc3b4fb3269b2d11f8ce8af0","tid":1448910,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">癱瘓香港</span></span>"}]}